<h2 style='margin-top:0cm'><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3. Database Schema Design (ER)<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

</div>

<p align=center style='text-align:center'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;color:#333333'>The relational database schema
is structured into three main tables: <b>users</b>, <b>properties</b>, and <b>leases</b>.
Below is the relational structure of the tables: <o:p></o:p></span></p>

