</div>

<div>

<div style='mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-bottom:solid #1F497D 1.5pt;
padding:0cm 0cm 3.0pt 0cm'>

<h2><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>4.
<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span>Architecture<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

</div>

<p align=center style='text-align:center'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;color:#333333;mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape
 id="Picture_x0020_6" o:spid="_x0000_i1029" type="#_x0000_t75" style='width:327.5pt;
 height:158.5pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>
 <v:imagedata src="Project_Report_files/image003.png" o:title="" cropbottom="8656f"/>
</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=437 height=211
src="Project_Report_files/image008.png" v:shapes="Picture_x0020_6"><![endif]></span><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;color:#333333'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p align=center style='text-align:center'><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;color:#333333'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<h3><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>4.1
Request Flow and Business Rules<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='color:#333333;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:
     6.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span
     style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Authentication Check</span></b><span style='font-size:
     11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>:
     Endpoint paths that require authentication use the <span class=SpellE><i>get_current_user</i></span>
     dependency, which decodes the JWT token from the HTTP Bearer header,
     validates it against the signing key, and retrieves the matching user
     record from the database.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='color:#333333;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:
     6.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span
     style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Role Restriction</span></b><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>:
     Landlord endpoints (e.g. creating/updating properties) are protected by <span
     class=SpellE><i>check_landlord</i></span>, which returns a 403 Forbidden
     error if a tenant tries to list a house.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='color:#333333;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:
     6.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span
     style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
     "Times New Roman"'>Lease Automation</span></b><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
     font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>:
     When a tenant successfully leases a property (`POST /leases`), the system
     automatically registers the lease in the database and updates the
     property's `<span class=SpellE>is_available</span>` column to `False`.
     When a lease is terminated (`POST /leases/{id}/terminate`), the property
     availability is set back to `True`.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

</div>

<div>

<div style='mso-element:para-border-div;border:none;border-bottom:solid #1F497D 1.5pt;
padding:0cm 0cm 3.0pt 0cm'>

<h2><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><!-- SECTION 5 -->5.
Postman Integration &amp; Testing Guide<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

</div>

<h3><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>5.1
Sign Up (`POST /signup`)<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<h3><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id="_x0000_i1028" type="#_x0000_t75"
 style='width:451.5pt;height:296.5pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>
 <v:imagedata src="Project_Report_files/image005.png" o:title=""/>
</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=602 height=395
src="Project_Report_files/image010.png" v:shapes="_x0000_i1028"><![endif]></span><span
style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><o:p></o:p></span></h3>

